{
  "stem": "11167.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew, because the radios and the news out of-- and the Russian must invade our part of-- where we-- in Dubno, our part.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went-- we ran away for 10 days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was after Rosh Hashanah, and 10 days to Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went away to a village-- to a-- just the whole family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't even lock the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything we-- everybody, we went away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed for 10 days, and then we hear that's the-- the Red Army is coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they don't touch anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't kill.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was between Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that this-- they straight away took away a room from us and, you know, other-- other things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was nothing to compare with what--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the Russian army that took over the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the Russian army, because we stayed-- in this street was the Polish army opposite, like-- like here the-- you see, like here the-- the houses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was our house, and that was the whole settling from the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the-- the Red Army took it-- hold of this position.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure you must have felt very safe living with the Red Army on the other side of the road to you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, we don't know safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we-- the stories what did go-- they will just take away the house, they will send them to Siberia-- you know, all these stories.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we just lived by year and by the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the-- the whole story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we did hear what is Hitler doing to the other side in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
